     Phase 4: Local Variables and Dynamic Arrays

     Overview

     Implement two critical debugger features:
     1. Local variables - Support for function parameters and local variables with stack-based addressing
     2. Dynamic arrays - Support for both static and dynamic arrays with proper length metadata

     Both features build on existing OPDF infrastructure (TDefLocalVar and TDefArray already defined) and follow the established type 
     evaluator pattern.

