     Potential Issues

     Issue 1: Signed offset parsing
     - Hex values 0x80-0xFF need sign extension
     - Mitigation: Use ShortInt typecast, test negative offsets

     Issue 2: Optimized code
     - Compiler may eliminate locals or use registers
     - Mitigation: Document -O0 requirement, test unoptimized builds

     Issue 3: Array bounds safety
     - Very large arrays could hang debugger
     - Mitigation: Limit reads to 10 elements, bounds-check lengths

     Issue 4: Dynamic array lifetime
     - Pointer may be stale after free
     - Mitigation: Validate pointer before reading metadata

     Issue 5: Multi-dimensional complexity
     - FPC uses row-major order
     - Mitigation: Start with 1D, test 2D carefully

